<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Grammy-nominated songstress Halsey celebrated her 26th birthday over a hearty Italian meal with friends at Giorgio Baldi in Santa Monica on Tuesday night.</p>

<p>The New Jersey-born pop star certainly looked leggy in a blue silk blouse, black PVC short shorts, and matching pumps for her special day.</p>

<p>Halsey made sure to protect herself and others from the coronavirus by wearing a matching blue mask, which California Governor Gavin Newsom made mandatory for public outings on June 18.   </p>

